text: Alena Polozkova (born 11 August 1979) is a Belarusian gymnast. She competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belarus Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Mogilev
